  "notes": [
    "This configuration resolves City of Litchfield Park zoning by intersecting runtime coordinates with Layer 0 of the current public LitchfieldPark_Zoning feature service.",
    "The City of Litchfield Park's official Planning and Zoning page links to the public GIS application that consumes this zoning layer, which is hosted through AZGeo.",
    "The query is restricted to JURISDICTION = 'LITCHFIELD PARK' because the source includes at least one parcel identified as outside a city or town.",
    "ZONING is the City-maintained zoning code. APN, situs address, general-plan land use, zoning ordinance, planned-development status, code setbacks, and special notes are retained when populated because they are directly relevant to permit research.",
    "Tax values, sale information, mailing addresses, and other assessor fields published by the layer are intentionally excluded from the query because they are not required for zoning or sign-permit review.",
    "District descriptions are normalized from the City of Litchfield Park Zoning Code and official zoning materials.",
    "The configured commercial fixture at The Wigwam, 300 E Wigwam Boulevard, resolves to APN 50164003B and RT, Resort.",
    "A zoning code containing PD identifies a Planned Development district; its controlling ordinance, development agreement, stipulations, or approved plans may govern signs and other development standards.",
    "A resolved zoning result supports permit research but does not replace review of applicable planned-development documents, zoning cases, ordinances, stipulations, overlays, Luke Air Force Base compatibility constraints, or confirmation by the City of Litchfield Park."
  ]
